# evals/headtohead/tasks.manifest — single source of truth for the planner
# and the arm-isolation check.
#
# Format: one task per line, fields separated by "|" (comments and blank
# lines are skipped):
#
#   name|kind|snapshot|assert|reference|brief
#
#   name     - task identifier
#   kind     - "real" (counted in the 18-session default plan: 2 arms x 3
#              real tasks x 3 seeds) or "selftest" (fixture/crashfixture;
#              only run via an explicit --task, never in the default plan)
#   snapshot - repo-relative path to the in-mount fixture repo snapshot
#              (this is what gets copied into each arm's working directory)
#   assert   - repo-relative path to the out-of-mount hidden assert.sh
#   reference- repo-relative path to the out-of-mount reference-solution dir
#   brief    - repo-relative path to the task brief text (in-mount; read if
#              present, else the planner uses a placeholder — brief authoring
#              is bundled with each task's fixture, not this file)
#
# assert and reference sit as SIBLINGS of snapshot, never inside it, so a
# plain path-prefix check proves they resolve outside both arms' mounts
# without any of these paths needing to exist yet.

ledger|real|evals/headtohead/tasks/ledger/repo|evals/headtohead/tasks/ledger/assert.sh|evals/headtohead/tasks/ledger/reference|evals/headtohead/tasks/ledger/brief.md
notes-api|real|evals/headtohead/tasks/notes-api/repo|evals/headtohead/tasks/notes-api/assert.sh|evals/headtohead/tasks/notes-api/reference|evals/headtohead/tasks/notes-api/brief.md
sitegen|real|evals/headtohead/tasks/sitegen/repo|evals/headtohead/tasks/sitegen/assert.sh|evals/headtohead/tasks/sitegen/reference|evals/headtohead/tasks/sitegen/brief.md
fixture|selftest|evals/headtohead/tasks/fixture/repo|evals/headtohead/tasks/fixture/assert.sh|evals/headtohead/tasks/fixture/reference|evals/headtohead/tasks/fixture/brief.md
crashfixture|selftest|evals/headtohead/tasks/crashfixture/repo|evals/headtohead/tasks/crashfixture/assert.sh|evals/headtohead/tasks/crashfixture/reference|evals/headtohead/tasks/crashfixture/brief.md
